{
  "stem": "23626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I used to be treated even more so because of my birthday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a lot of nice things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing as elaborate that we buy for our grandchildren now, but there was always something special that meant to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's-- it's hard even to remember exactly what it was, but I know that it was always something special given to me by my parents, my grandmother, my aunts.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It's-- thinking back about those times, it's incredible how happy they were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was just too bad they were so short-lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But they left me with a very happy outlook in life, in spite of everything, that I am counted.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I do have this in-- this urge for life and-- and it must be-- have a lot to do with my upbringing, I think.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I shared my room with my sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we didn't have such elaborate home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I shared with my two sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember my corner where I had my bed and my dolls and my carriage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it wasn't a home like I live in now, but it was a love-- loving home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a cozy home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was my home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had, you know-- well, like, three rooms and a kitchen, with a dining room and my parent's bedroom and our bedroom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a very large kitchen, which we spent most of the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Very cheerful, very warm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those are my happy memories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And prior to it, where I was born as a little girl, I-- we lived mostly between non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were only three Jewish families which we were very close to, but my-- my-- my parents were very close with the-- with the Gentile neighbors.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
